      • getChromeDriver

        private static org.openqa.selenium.WebDriver getChromeDriver()
        Returns Chrome driver instance. if ConfigProperties.USEWEBDRIVERMANAGER='yes', then the driver instance is crated using WebDriverManager, else local chrome executable is used.
        Returns:
        chrome driver instance

        Firefox driver instance.
